=Description=

George Por:

"we want to prototype a new way, in which women, men and youth can co-create sustainable and scalable solutions to vexing social ills at the root of all our crises, informed by both the consciousness of humankind's inherent unity, and breakthroughs in domain expertise.

We call that way “World-Citizen Panels” that we need to build as we walk on it. “World-citizen” refers to people who choose to think, sense, and act from the largest Whole that they can put their arms around."
(http://www.worldcitizenpanels.org/notes/About_our_initiative)


